    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering power through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Technical highlights include a recently completed VANOS solenoid overhaul and comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The valvetrain is quiet, and the individual throttle bodies provide the signature induction note and immediate throttle response expected of this platform. The suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein B6 dampers and polyurethane bushings for improved lateral stability. While the paint shows minor road rash consistent with use, the mechanical vitals are sorted, making this an ideal driver\u2019s car for the purist who prioritizes performance over garage-queen status.",
      "price": 32500.0,
